Control Manager
===============

    - Controller continuously manages the status of various components of the system

    Node Controller - Status of the Nodes
    -------------------------------------
    
    Watch Status
    Remediate Situation
    Node Monitor Period = 5s 
    Node Montior Grace Period = 40s
    After that node is marker unreachable
    POD Eviction Timeout - 5mins



    Replication Controller:
    -----------------------

        - Ensures the numbers of replicasets are maintained
